<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">قال:</span> حدَّثناه <span class="c1">"أبو معاوية"</span> عن <span class="c1">"حجَّاج بن أرطاة"</span> عن <span class="c1">"الزُّهرىِّ"</span> يرفعه.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">قوله:</span> <span class="c1">"لا تولَّه والدة عن ولدها"</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>